<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="..\config8\suzuki.xsl" ?><!DOCTYPE suzuki [<!ENTITY % sdatacharaents SYSTEM "..\config8\sdatacharaents.txt">%sdatacharaents;]><suzuki><manual>
<section sectnbr = "1J">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "10">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "4">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENCP70A1A04003" svcinfotypenbr = "06" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Generator Test
</title>
<ptxt>
This condition, as evidenced by slow cranking or low specific gravity, can be caused by one or more of the following conditions even though warning light may be operating normal. The following procedure also applies to cars with voltmeter and ammeter.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Make sure that undercharged condition has not been caused by accessories being left on for extended period of time.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check drive belt for wear and tension. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1A06003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
If battery defect is suspected, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A1A01001">Battery Description</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Inspect wiring for defects. Check all connections for tightness and cleanliness, battery cable connections at battery, starting motor and ignition ground cable.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A1A04003001">
<title>
No-Load Check
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Use fully charged battery.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check for DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1104003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If there is any DTC, perform troubleshooting for applicable DTC and then clear DTC.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Troubleshooting: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1104005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
DTC clearance: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1104004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Turn off all electrical loads (5).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect voltmeter (3) and ammeter (2) as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine and warm it up to normal operating temperature.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A1A1018.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.952mm" ver = "01" gw = "198" gh = "119"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.299in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.842in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.299in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.903in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Generator
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
6.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Switch
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
4.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Battery
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
7.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
“B” terminal
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Run engine around 2,000 rpm and read meters.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
If voltage is higher than standard value, check ground circuit of brushes. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1A06009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If brushes are not grounded, replace IC regulator.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
If voltage is lower than standard value, inspect rotor, stator, rectifier, bushings and regulator. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A1A06009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<spec>
<title>
Specification for undercharged battery (No-load check)
</title>
<ptxt>
Current: 10 A 
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Regulated voltage: 11.7 – 15.3 V (at 25 &#176;C, 77 &#176;F)
</ptxt>
</spec>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A1A04003002">
<title>
Load Check
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Use fully charged battery.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Connect ammeter in the same way as 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A1A04003001">No-Load Check</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Run engine around 2,000 rpm and turn on the following electrical loads.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Headlight (High beam)
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Rear window defogger
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Blower motor (Maximum speed)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Read ammeter.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If meter reading is less than 20 A, repair or replace generator.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
